<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <meta name="color-scheme" content="light only">
    <meta name="supported-color-schemes" content="light only">
  </head>
  <body style="margin: 0; padding: 24px; background-color: #f3f4f6; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #1f2937;">
    <table role="presentation" width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <table role="presentation" width="600" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="max-width: 600px; width: 100%; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
            <tr>
              <td bgcolor="#7c3aed" style="background-color: #7c3aed; padding: 24px;">
                <span style="display: inline-block; background-color: #ffffff33; color: #ffffff; font-weight: 700; font-size: 11px; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 999px; letter-spacing: 0.6px; text-transform: uppercase;">NUEVO REGISTRO</span>
                <h1 style="margin: 12px 0 4px; color: #ffffff; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700;">🎉 Nuevo registro en la plataforma</h1>
                <p style="margin: 0; color: #ffffff; opacity: 0.9; font-size: 14px;">Acaba de crear su cuenta un nuevo usuario en Tivo.</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 24px; background-color: #ffffff;">
                <p style="margin: 0 0 12px;">Hola owner, te avisamos que se ha registrado un nuevo usuario:</p>

                <table role="presentation" width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-top: 16px;">
                  <tr>
                    <th align="left" style="padding: 10px 0; width: 32%; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6; color: #6b7280; font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600;">Email</th>
                    <td style="padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6; color: #111827; font-size: 15px;"><%= @user.email %></td>
                  </tr>
                  <% if @user.full_name.to_s.strip.present? %>
                    <tr>
                      <th align="left" style="padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6; color: #6b7280; font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600;">Nombre</th>
                      <td style="padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6; color: #111827; font-size: 15px;"><%= @user.full_name %></td>
                    </tr>
                  <% end %>
                  <tr>
                    <th align="left" style="padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6; color: #6b7280; font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600;">Origen</th>
                    <td style="padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6; color: #111827; font-size: 15px;">
                      <%= @user.provider.present? ? @user.provider.titleize : "Email + contraseña" %>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <th align="left" style="padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6; color: #6b7280; font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600;">ID</th>
                    <td style="padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6; color: #111827; font-size: 15px;">#<%= @user.id %></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <th align="left" style="padding: 10px 0; color: #6b7280; font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600;">Fecha</th>
                    <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: #111827; font-size: 15px;">
                      <%= l(@user.created_at, format: :long) rescue @user.created_at.strftime("%d/%m/%Y %H:%M") %>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td align="center" style="padding: 16px 24px 24px; color: #9ca3af; font-size: 12px; background-color: #ffffff;">
                Notificación automática de Tivo · No respondas a este correo.
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
